2.0 of this extension with new features. First, when you click on "Select Audio File", you will now see an "All Folders" option. You can select audio files from any folder and search for them there. Second, filter options have been added so you can filter audios by weekly or monthly. Third, when you double-click on any audio file it will play, and if you double-click again on the same audio it will pause. Fourth, if you want to select any audio file, you need to long press on it. These new features have been added in this extension.